name: Lucid Mandala Dreams 01
description: Primary Nature Lucid Mandala Dreams 01 is a piece which delves into the occurrence of an artwork floating so long in the noise on Opensea that it falls asleep and begins to dream. This dream happens to be a lucid one and now the work finds itself in a new and unfamiliar but pleasing environment on hitetnunc. More vibrant and looser now this work would rather remain here, content and asleep, dreaming. Take this slumbering artwork for yourself and nurture it's state of rest.
